  "texts": [
    "On the other hand, KNN, SVM, and MLP yielded the lowest performance which was below 30% of test accuracy.",
    "From these results, it observed that DT, RF, and XGBoost is a potential and an effective approaches to tackling abrasive belt grinding problems.",
    "For the efficient models, DT and XGBoost produced the lowest latency compared to other models.",
    "Both models achieved a computational time of roughly 0.004 s for running the test set.",
    "Meanwhile, XGBoost provided the highest latency with approximately 0.02 s which becomes the lowest performance among all models."
  ]
